# Basic JavaScript: An Introduction to The Language
http://www.2ality.com/2013/06/basic-javascript.html
This blog post enables you to get started with JavaScript as quickly as po=
ssible =E2=80=93 if you already know how to program. It describes the smal=
lest subset of the language that allows you to be productive. Perhaps one=
 to forward on to other team members?
